msgid "Set up a PIN\n"
"A Hello PIN is a fast, secure way to sign in to your device, apps, and services."
msgstr "PIN qopheessi\n"
"PIN Hello mala saffisaa fi nageenya qabu kan meeshaa kee, appoota, fi tajaajiloota seenuuf gargaarudha."

